ility of", "bbox": [143.8, 1222.0, 1047.6, 1242.9]}, {"text": "Tyco Electronics to pay dividends.", "bbox": [143.8, 1247.0, 452.9, 1267.9]}, {"text": "Performance Graph", "bbox": [143.8, 1297.1, 324.3, 1317.9]}, {"text": "Set forth below is a graph comparing the cumulative total shareholder return on Tyco Electronics’", "bbox": [185.5, 1334.6, 1080.3, 1355.4]}, {"text": "common shares against the cumulative return on the S&P 500 Index and the Dow Jones Wilshire", "bbox": [143.8, 1359.6, 1033.5, 1380.4]}, {"text": "Electrical Components & Equipment Index, assuming investment of $100 on June 14, 2007, the first", "bbox": [143.8, 1384.6, 1058.6, 1405.4]}, {"text": "30", "bbox": [143.8, 1469.0, 160.5, 1485.7]}, {"text": "2008 Form 10-K", "bbox": [193.8, 1469.0, 312.2, 1485.7]}]}